  'Toss with tomatoes, cucumber, spring onions, parsley, mint and pomegranate seeds.',
  'Dress with lemon juice and olive oil. Season with salt and pepper.',
]},

{id:34,name:'Warm Farro Salad with Roasted Capsicum & Herbs',category:'Salads',difficulty:'easy',serves:2,time:'30 min',calories:360,mainIngredient:'Farro',
